snippet.title: Monster Hunter Wilds - Launch Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Pre-order now: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10005176/
 
Prepare for thrilling hunts on the horizon and beyond with the latest Monster Hunter Wilds pre-launch trailer, set to the signature series theme: "Proof of a Hero."
 
The next generation of Capcom's critically acclaimed series begins on PS5, February 28, 2025. 

#ps5 #ps5games #monsterhunterwilds #stateofplay
